Along the Silk Road: Joy Bostwick--The Silk Road Artist
You can also click here to watch this video and more.
American artist Joy Bostwick arrived in Xinjiang Uygur Autonomous Region three years ago. To date, she has finished more than 40 paintings in Xinjiang, showing the beautiful nature and unique culture in this place. But traditional styles of life are dying as Xinjiang develops. Joy knows that her paintings document the beauty before it all disappears.
The American artist, Joy Bostwick documents the beauty of Xinjiang with her paintings.[Photo: CRIENGLISH.com] 